Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Import errors for pandas/matplotlib

pip3 install --upgrade pandas matplotlib seaborn numpy
Issue: Empty DataFrames or missing data

Verify all TODO sections are implemented
Check that CSV files exist before loading
Ensure proper data types in calculations
Issue: Visualization not saving

Confirm matplotlib backend: python3 -c "import matplotlib; print(matplotlib.get_backend())"
Add plt.close() after each save
Check write permissions in directory
Issue: JSON serialization errors

Convert numpy types to Python types: float(value), int(value)
Use default=str in json.dump() for datetime objects
